# app.js Patterns

Single-file imperative JS. Follow existing structure:

1. Constants (`STORAGE_KEY`, `lifts`, `defaultProfile`) at top
2. One-time event listeners
3. Pure helpers → `buildPlan` / `prescription` → `render*` → persistence utils

Rendering: template strings into innerHTML. Match class names from `styles.css`.

Weights: always `roundLoad()` for display/storage. Unit change → `convertStoredWeights()` then `rebuildPlanIfPossible()`.

Plan changes: edit `buildWeeks()`, `buildSessions()` weekPlans, and `lifts` map together.

New lift checklist: `lifts` object → `#maxForm` input → weekPlans prescriptions → test import/export.

Check IDs: `` `${lift.name}-${index}` `` — changing breaks saved `todayChecks`.
